## Budget Limits

| Limit | Value | What Happens If Exceeded |
|-------|-------|-------------------------|
| Max files changed | {{ budgets.max_files_changed }} | Mission fails with BUDGET stop condition |
| Max scenarios promoted | {{ budgets.max_scenarios_promoted }} | Mission fails with BUDGET stop condition |
| Max runtime (seconds) | {{ budgets.max_runtime_seconds }} | Runner process killed, BUDGET stop condition |
| Max retries | {{ budgets.max_retries }} | Mission fails after this many attempts |

## Validation

After you exit, Tesaki will:

1. Run `namako gate --json` to validate your changes
2. Check that budgets were not exceeded
3. Record results to `POST_GATE.json`

Your `attempt_report.md` is informational only — success is determined by the gate result.

